<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>页面未找到 ｜ {{ site_name }}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="页面未找到">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="{{ site.theme_color }}">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex">
  {% if site_url %}
  <link rel="canonical" href="{{ site_url }}/404.html">
  {% endif %}
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles/gallery.css?v={{ static_version }}">
</head>
<body class="page-error page-404">
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main-content">跳到主要内容</a>
  <header class="topbar">
    <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="返回首页">
      <span class="logo-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <div class="brand-text">
        <strong>{{ site.brand_name or site_name }}</strong>
        <span>{{ site.brand_tagline }}</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <nav class="topnav" aria-label="顶栏导航">
      <a href="/">首页</a>
      <a href="/status/">运行状态</a>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <main id="main-content" class="error-main" tabindex="-1">
    <section class="error-hero">
      <div class="error-card">
        <div class="error-eyebrow">很抱歉</div>
        <h1 class="error-title">您浏览的页面走丢了</h1>
        <p class="error-lead">页面可能已被移动、删除，或地址输入有误。为此带来的不便，我们向您致歉。</p>
        <div class="error-actions">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/">回到首页</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="/search/">重新搜索</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="/status/">查看状态</a>
        </div>
        <div class="error-meta">
          <span class="error-code">404</span>
          <span class="error-tag">Not Found</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <figure class="error-figure">
        <div class="error-figure-frame">
          <img src="/static/images/error-figure.webp" alt="迷路的小人插画" width="950" height="1200" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        </div>
        <figcaption>如果你是从收藏或分享链接进入，地址可能已经更新。</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </section>
    <section class="error-tips" aria-label="提示">
      <div class="error-tip">
        <h2>提示</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>检查地址是否有多余字符或大小写错误。</li>
          <li>尝试使用搜索找回作品、标签或画廊。</li>
          <li>如果页面持续不可用，可稍后刷新或查看状态页。</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="error-tip">
        <h2>推荐操作</h2>
        <p>返回首页重新浏览，或使用搜索与标签导航快速定位内容。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="error-tip">
        <h2>需要帮助？</h2>
        <p>请保留本页截图和错误码 404，便于我们定位问题。</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <script src="/static/js/ui.js?v={{ static_version }}" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
